    "There are typically two types of segmentation methods, namely context-dependent and context-independent.",
    "Context-sensitive segmentation considers the spatial relationship between features, such as edge detection technology.",
    "Context-free does not consider spatial relations but groups pixels based on global attributes.",
    "The rise of deep learning brings new opportunities to sign language segmentation.",
    "After massive data training, the model completes the corresponding sign language segmentation, making the segmentation more convenient and having good application prospects in sign language segmentation."
